item.description:
@srfsdfsd wrote:

[quote=“Davidi2, post:171, topic:391723”][quote author=srfsdfsd link=topic=488887.msg4379268#msg4379268 date=1383016876]

[quote author=Davidi2 link=topic=488887.msg4376115#msg4376115 date=1382077489]

When does this update becuase it’s old

Its never going to update
[/quote]^ this
it’s so much harder to update without mod powers to edit posts and delete the topics that mess up my list generator

Plus, the majority of the downloads are dead now.
Such a waste…
[/quote]That’s a bit of an exaggeration. The reason downloads are dead has nothing to do with how recently the list has been updated. The sites remove them or shut down and I can’t check that easily. I will update this again soon though because I am a mod again, but even still your post is a bit dramatic.[/quote]

I did not mean for that reply to come across like that, what I was trying to say that there is one hell of a load of server/client downloads here that are done due to expired links, fileshare sites shutting down and downloads being removed due to the copyright law. I understand that it’s not your fault.

However on a positive note, congratulations on your promotion and I am glad that you are going to resort this thread out. All in all, I bet this was one hell of a topic back in it’s day. Good job.
